matrix_3d[nd][ni][nj] - indices: d, i, j
matrix_3d[d][i][j]=matrix_3d[(d*ni*nj) + (i*nj) + j]

Indices to 1d-array:
d=index/(ni*nj)
i=(index/nj)%ni
j=index%nj
'''

